as Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 31, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessGUI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31692\">ChessGUI 0.173 is out</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 13, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31952\">ChessGUI 0.175 is out</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 23, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32521\">ChessGUI 0.176 is out there</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 10, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32884\">ChessGUI 0.178 is out there</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 24, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32904\">ChessGUI ... UCI ... Gaviota EGTB</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 25, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Gaviota_Tablebases\" title=\"Gaviota Tablebases\">Gaviota Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=